---
title: Smart Shrimp and Salmon Curry with Buttered Couscous
description: This silky, fragrant curry sauce built with warm spices, tomatoes and cream cheese is sure to delight your palate! A healthy serving of shrimp, salmon and a side of light couscous make this meal a wholesome wonder.

Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie and carbohydrate amount.
